        <headline>Severe Thunderstorm Warning issued July 7 at 10:31PM CDT until July 7 at 11:00PM CDT by NWS Amarillo TX</headline>
        <description>At 1031 PM CDT, severe thunderstorms were located along a line
extending from 5 miles southwest of Simms to 4 miles east of Bootleg
to 7 miles north of Friona, moving southeast at 25 mph.

HAZARD...60 mph wind gusts and penny size hail.

SOURCE...Radar indicated.

IMPACT...Minor damage to roofs, siding, and trees is possible.

Locations impacted include...
Bootleg.
</description>
        <instruction>For your protection move to an interior room on the lowest floor of a
building.</instruction>
